Our support pathway is:

2. HubSpot Premier Consulting Team (Amy Broman, Nathanael Yellis)
3. HubSpot Support Direct
Our end users (sales reps and sales managers) direct all their support questions to <mailto:sales.ops@e-arc.com|sales.ops@e-arc.com>. This is monitored by Kari Fairbanks and me.

If we can’t resolve their issue, Kari or Frank then escalate the issue to Amy and Nathanael.

If they aren’t able to answer or resolve the issue, we then escalate it directly to HubSpot support team via the website.
